						               													<description>Have you always dreamt of being one of the thieves in Ocean's Eleven? Or perhaps with participating in the Sting? Would you like to be a cat burglar and live la dolce vitta? Then Theft of the Century is the game for you!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Your mission in Theft of the Century will be to escape the police hunting you at every turn. The police will be faster or slower depending on the cards played by your opponents. With a hand management system where you can draw or play cards to make your thief run faster, that make the police quicker when chasing your rivals, and that will combine with each other to earn you points. Play hidden cards to solve at the end of each round, trump your opponent&amp;rsquo;s strategies and get the most valuable booty!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is played in a variable number of rounds, with an objective card that marks the end of the game. Players will use their cards and solve their effects, up to a maximum of 4 cards each round per player. The player who achieves more objectives will be the winner of the game. Will you be the thief who performs the Theft of the Century?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;iquest;Siempre so&amp;ntilde;aste con ser uno de los ladrones de Ocean&amp;rsquo;s Eleven? &amp;iquest;O tal vez con participar en El Golpe? &amp;iquest;Te gustar&amp;iacute;a ser un ladr&amp;oacute;n de guante blanco y vivir la dolce vittta? &amp;iexcl;Entonces El Robo del Siglo es el juego para ti!.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;En el Robo del Siglo tu misi&amp;oacute;n ser&amp;aacute; huir de la polic&amp;iacute;a que intentar&amp;aacute; darte caza en cuanto tenga ocasi&amp;oacute;n. La polic&amp;iacute;a ser&amp;aacute; m&amp;aacute;s r&amp;aacute;pida o m&amp;aacute;s lenta en funci&amp;oacute;n de las cartas que vayan jugando tus compa&amp;ntilde;eros. Con un sistema de gesti&amp;oacute;n de mano de cartas donde podr&amp;aacute;s robar o jugar cartas que har&amp;aacute;n que tu ladr&amp;oacute;n corra m&amp;aacute;s, que la polic&amp;iacute;a persiga m&amp;aacute;s r&amp;aacute;pido a tus rivales, y que har&amp;aacute;n combos entre s&amp;iacute; para conseguir puntos. Apuesta cartas ocultas para resolver al final de cada ronda, entorpece a los ladrones enemigos y &amp;iexcl;consigue el bot&amp;iacute;n m&amp;aacute;s valioso!.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;El juego consta de un n&amp;uacute;mero de rondas variables en funci&amp;oacute;n de una carta objetivo que marca el final de la partida. Los jugadores ir&amp;aacute;n jugando cartas y resolviendo sus efectos, hasta un m&amp;aacute;ximo de 4 turnos por ronda y por jugador. El jugador que consiga m&amp;aacute;s objetivos ser&amp;aacute; el ganador de la partida &amp;iquest;Ser&amp;aacute;s t&amp;uacute; el ladr&amp;oacute;n que consiga realizar El Robo del Siglo?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher (Spanish)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
